    <item>
      <title>美联储库格勒表示她“强烈支持”降息半个百分点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/fed-s-kugler-says-she-strongly-supported-half-point-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事阿德里安娜·库格勒表示，她“强烈支持”央行上周将借贷成本降低半个百分点的决定，并补充说，如果通胀继续如预期般缓解，进一步降息将是适当的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/fed-s-kugler-says-she-strongly-supported-half-point-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
